WEBVTT

00:00:03.801 --> 00:00:07.554
But as Kundalini rises, on every center

00:00:07.634 --> 00:00:10.854
you start getting the light of that center.

00:00:10.934 --> 00:00:15.920
At the first center you get back your innocence,

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.920
your eyes become innocent,
your behavior becomes innocent,

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.554
you are not filled with lust and greed,

00:00:25.634 --> 00:00:28.654
you don’t look at things with lust and greed,

00:00:28.734 --> 00:00:31.920
but you look at things with innocence,

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.920
which is a very big thing that people have lost

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.854
and that you get back and such
a person develops many qualities.

00:00:40.934 --> 00:00:46.154
One of them is that such a person is full of fragrance,

00:00:46.234 --> 00:00:51.920
such a person has a tremendous gravity,

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:57.953
tremendous gravity, and such a
person has tremendous dynamism,

00:00:58.033 --> 00:01:02.454
and attraction is a bad word so I don’t want to use it,

00:01:02.534 --> 00:01:04.920
but  magnetic.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:08.854
His magnets is awakened within him,

00:01:08.934 --> 00:01:13.920
this is the center of your magnet of the earth.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:19.920
Such a person develops a tremendous sense of  roads

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.987
and sense of direction, you place him anywhere

00:01:23.067 --> 00:01:27.587
he will know where to go. Like
birds, you place birds anywhere

00:01:27.667 --> 00:01:30.554
they know which side is north, south, east, west.

00:01:30.634 --> 00:01:35.987
In the same way you also develop your lost innocence

00:01:36.067 --> 00:01:41.920
and your magnet within you, by
which you have proper direction;

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:46.920
but the highest of all you develop the proper direction

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:50.320
to wisdom which is the wise thing to do.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:54.920
You just don’t do stupid things, you just don’t do,

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:58.254
even if you ever try to do it, you will not do it,

00:01:58.334 --> 00:02:03.587
because you know it is so stupid, just you don’t do it.

00:02:03.667 --> 00:02:09.154
I mean it is so simple to be wise than to be stupid,

00:02:09.234 --> 00:02:12.920
because if you have to be stupid
you have to go out of the way

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:17.920
to be stupid and idiotic; but if you want to be

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:21.000
normal and wise is the easiest thing to do.

00:02:22.067 --> 00:02:25.854
If Shri Ganesha is within you become like a child,

00:02:25.934 --> 00:02:31.254
childlike innocence, you don’t get angry with somebody

00:02:31.334 --> 00:02:33.987
like a dog barks; there are some Sahaja Yogis I know

00:02:34.067 --> 00:02:39.000
who all the time barking, just
like dogs or beggars in India.

00:02:44.067 --> 00:02:48.987
But you become like a child who is very sweet,

00:02:49.067 --> 00:02:51.920
who always tries to amuse you,

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:54.920
always tries to say nice things,

00:02:55.000 --> 00:03:00.067
always tries to make you feel
happy. The source of such joy.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:08.920
And that’s how you become a source of joy,

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:15.000
source of happiness, source of fulfilment.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:22.454
So this, this centre

00:03:22.534 --> 00:03:26.387
that is what we call the Swadishthana centre

00:03:26.467 --> 00:03:32.987
is the centre that gives you your future

00:03:33.067 --> 00:03:37.888
energy to think of your future, your planning;

00:03:37.968 --> 00:03:40.920
which gives you energy to bring forth

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:42.987
the manifestation of the physical labor,

00:03:43.067 --> 00:03:47.554
of physical exercise or physical work.

00:03:47.634 --> 00:03:50.888
This poor centre has to work for one work:

00:03:50.968 --> 00:03:54.000
to convert the fat for the use of the brain.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:04:00.920
Now, if one centre which has to do many other things

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:04.920
starts doing only one work,
all other things are neglected.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:08.987
As a result of that you develop problems,

00:04:09.067 --> 00:04:13.788
because it has to cater to
your liver, to your pancreas,

00:04:13.868 --> 00:04:17.067
to your kidneys, to your spleen,

00:04:18.567 --> 00:04:27.987
and once it goes into action for one channelized work

00:04:28.067 --> 00:04:30.387
it gets programmed for it,

00:04:30.467 --> 00:04:33.254
and then it cannot take care of these things.

00:04:33.334 --> 00:04:35.920
That’s how you develop a bad liver,

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:40.920
you develop a diabetes,

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.920
kidney trouble, blood pressures.

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:50.000
