When the Kundalini awakens itself,

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:58.254
She makes the centre enlightened

00:04:58.334 --> 00:05:03.387
and the centre itself resumes its normal shape,

00:05:03.467 --> 00:05:07.920
its normal behaviour and its normal condition.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:16.320
Apart from that it has got a dynamic power

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:19.920
or manifestation that this one,

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:23.000
this centre which looks after our attention

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:28.554
becomes enlightened, and our
attention becomes enlightened,

00:05:28.634 --> 00:05:32.920
and the attention which is enlightened becomes dynamic

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:37.053
in the sense now, sitting down
here you can pay attention to anyone

00:05:37.133 --> 00:05:39.854
– just pay attention, you don’t have to do anything,

00:05:39.934 --> 00:05:41.920
just pay attention to that person,

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:46.000
and you can find out on your fingertips
what’s the matter with the person.

